{"tid":862688,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"［15/10］［等鞭屍］陸東：港股已夠平　已喺二萬五附近買騰訊、港交所！","createTime":"2018-10-15T04:28:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T05:15:46.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"403565e23868e22d5fe993b8a9513411664cd085","tid":862688,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T04:28:27.000Z","msg":"上周恆指單日曾下跌過千點，整個星期累計下挫771點，跌幅2.9%，連續三星期下跌，市場一片愁雲慘霧。但星級分析師、中港通資產管理首席投資總監陸東，接受《iMoney》雜誌專訪時就指，已於港股見25,000點附近，身體力行分注購入5隻愛股。<br />\n<br />\n他在訪問中表示，購入股份中包括股王騰訊(700)、港交所(388)等。他指出：「因為（港）股票夠平，所以入市，而美股貴，但認為未見頂。」他指會分注購入中港兩地的股票，指現時跌下來可以買，如跌穿25,000點的話，會繼續增持。<br />\n<br />\n早前訪問中，他指：「騰訊落到300蚊左右先好入」；又預測香港樓市「下半年會差過上半年，今年高位已見，但要跌又好難！」。今次訪問中，他就預料人民幣很快就會穿七算，而樓市周期已見頂，銀行亦會主動下調大型私人屋苑估價，幅度最高達5%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181014/58793929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181014%2F58793929&d=unlMM%2FuKD%2FK3TerAu3X8VGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=e5f7ddc5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181014%2F58793929&h=81678ba4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181014/58793929</a>"},{"pid":"d54f56c783416c186a08d8321231ddf0934fce42","tid":862688,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T04:32:44.000Z","msg":"陸東<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66f31874e68bc6cd027aa2b21b9f7ee682068805","tid":862688,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T04:32:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"> 又預測香港樓市「下半年會差過上半年，今年高位已見，但要跌又好難！」</span><br />\n唔計派？"},{"pid":"ce130c6c939d4687aeb6bd8078d821d6bfa3f427","tid":862688,"uid":84771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T04:38:04.000Z","msg":"燈燈燈燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bi